# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:80
translate chinese adrianphone_9e6d7a2e:

    # pc "I was just wondering if you were free to come over and help with my dad's laptop."
    pc "我正想问你有没有空过来帮我修我爸的笔记本电脑。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:83
translate chinese adrianphone_1f602bfd:

    # gg "It's a little late right now. Could we do it sometime earlier in the day?"
    gg "现在有点晚了。我们能不能改在白天早点的时候？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:84
translate chinese adrianphone_325243c6:

    # pc "Sure, you're right. Okay, I'll call you some other day when it's earlier."
    pc "好的，你说得对。行，等哪天早点的时候我再给你打电话。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:85
translate chinese adrianphone_5e17d929:

    # gg "Okay, sorry, [pcname]. I'll talk to you later, okay?"
    gg "好的，抱歉，[pcname]。回头再聊，行吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:89
translate chinese adrianphone_5a61ec4b:

    # gg "I don't really have time to do it before school."
    gg "上学前我真的没时间做这个。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:90
translate chinese adrianphone_8ec59c74:

    # gg "Could you give me a call after school maybe?"
    gg "放学后你能给我打个电话吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:91
translate chinese adrianphone_55b46fe0:

    # pc "Oh sure, you're right."
    pc "哦，好的，你说得对。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:92
translate chinese adrianphone_71abeb5f:

    # gg "Sorry, [pcname]. I'll talk to you later, okay?"
    gg "抱歉，[pcname]。等会儿再聊，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:97
translate chinese adrianphone_ec536340:

    # pc "Hey. I wanted to talk to you about something."
    pc "嘿。我想跟你谈点事。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:98
translate chinese adrianphone_f6964fe7:

    # pc "Before, I thought that I just wanted to be friends with you."
    pc "之前，我以为我只想和你做朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:99
translate chinese adrianphone_3edf6017:

    # pc "But now... I think I want something more."
    pc "但现在……我觉得我想要更多。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:101
translate chinese adrianphone_2087cf83:

    # gg "Oh, really? What's changed?"
    gg "哦，真的吗？有什么变化吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:102
translate chinese adrianphone_6e39417e:

    # pc "I don't know... I just really like you, Adrian. I want to try this, if that's okay."
    pc "我也不知道……我就是真的很喜欢你，阿德里安。如果可以的话，我想试一试。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:104
translate chinese adrianphone_017e8feb:

    # gg "Okay. We can try it."
    gg "好的。我们可以试试。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:106
translate chinese adrianphone_d73ac63a:

    # gg "But only because I really like you too."
    gg "不过，也是因为我也真的很喜欢你。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:107
translate chinese adrianphone_b932f712:

    # pc "Thank you. I'm glad to hear that."
    pc "谢谢。听到这个我很高兴。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:108
translate chinese adrianphone_aa5d791d:

    # gg "Awesome. I'm looking forward to spending some more time with you then."
    gg "太棒了。那我期待能多陪陪你。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:109
translate chinese adrianphone_03eaad50:

    # pc "Me too."
    pc "我也是。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:111
translate chinese adrianphone_07141454:

    # gg "I should go for now though."
    gg "不过我得先走了。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:112
translate chinese adrianphone_e18c7fe2:

    # pc "Oh, okay. I'll talk to you later then."
    pc "哦，好的。那我们待会儿再聊。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:113
translate chinese adrianphone_01aff264:

    # gg "Okay. Bye, [pcname]."
    gg "好的。再见，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianPhone/adrianphone.rpy:118
translate chinese adrianphone_8d9bed8f:

    # gg "Okay then, talk to you later."
